\v 20 <a name="00501102000004" ll="SDBH:כתב:000000:Write|Know" il="WritingScroll-ReedPen-01-065d;tb032014452">Напиши</a> их на дверных <a name="00501102000008" ll="SDBH:מְזוּזָה:000000:Parts: Constructions" il="Realia:3.1.2.4">косяках</a> твоего <a name="00501102000010" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000:Buildings" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20140917;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a">дома</a> и на <a name="00501102000016" ll="SDBH:שַׁעַר:000000:Parts: Constructions" il="Realia:3.13.3.5b;Tel_Arad;CityGate-03-042c;Bolen00142;Bolen00143">городских</a> воротах.
